@startuml
title Diagrama de Estados - Round (Estado Atual)

[*] --> Setup

Setup : RoundSetupState
Setup : cria deck, embaralha,
Setup : revela trunfo e distribui cartas
Setup --> Playing : emite ROUND_STARTED

Playing : RoundPlayingState
Playing : gere trick atual e turnos
Playing --> Playing : CARD_PLAYED/TURN_CHANGED
Playing --> Playing : trick termina e inicia nova trick
Playing --> Finished : todas as mãos vazias

Finished : RoundFinishedState
Finished : emite ROUND_ENDED
Finished --> [*]

@enduml
